s=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">↥<span class=\"fn\">I</span></span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">X</span> <span class=\"fn\">(↑<span class=\"fn\">x</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">ω</span></span></span></span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Integral/Bochner/Basic.html#MeasureTheory.integral\">∂</a><span class=\"fn\">P</span>)</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a>         <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Integral/Bochner/Basic.html#MeasureTheory.integral\">∫</a> (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Ω</span>)<a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Integral/Bochner/Basic.html#MeasureTheory.integral\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">ω</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Ω</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">g</span> <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">↥<span class=\"fn\">J</span></span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">Y</span> <span class=\"fn\">(↑<span class=\"fn\">x</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">ω</span></span></span></span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Integral/Bochner/Basic.html#MeasureTheory.integral\">∂</a><span class=\"fn\">P</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Probability/Independence/Basic.html#ProbabilityTheory.IndepFun\">ProbabilityTheory.IndepFun</a> <span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">ω</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Ω</span>) (<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\">S</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">X</span> <span class=\"fn\">s</span> <span class=\"fn\">ω</span></span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">ω</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Ω</span>) (<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <span class=\"fn\">T</span